sosreport tool to collect system profile including hardware profile.

/etc/sos.conf              : configuration file (disbale plugins)

sosreport    -l               : list of plugins (enabled/disbaled)
             --list-profiles  : list all profiles
             -o=<plugins>     : only plugins
             -n=<no_plugons>  : disable plugin
             -p               : specify a profle from existing ones
             --tmp-dir=<dir>  : specify another tmp directory
